social_posts.post_text:
Whistler while you work 🇨🇦🏔️⛷️

Slowly collecting ski week gigs like infinity stones.

One of the best weekends of my life ❤️.

I don’t think I’ve ever met a more incredible collection of people. And then getting to dance the night away (and the morning in) with everyone to the best music - a one of a kind experience. 

Thank you @takemetoutopia, @jakeresnicow, and the entire rest of the team that made this happen. Each year gets better and better!
Mexico City on film 📸

Never trust a DJ that doesn’t dance 🙅🏻‍♂️

Still glowing from our @p.l.a.y.h.a.u.s event this weekend. We sold out one of Denver’s coolest venues!

Pics coming soon 📸

Next event is June 2 ;)

📸 by @simplyhao

“Here, why don’t you DJ” - POV you ask me for a song request. 

Had a blast shooting with @ragoimages during my 16 hours in DC last week!

Whirlwind of a weekend. 🙌

Started off closing on the 18th story of @lebainnyc in NY, then joined @tysunderland for some disco at @3dollarbillbk.

Last minute decided to travel down to DC to see my favs play at Project Glow fest, and spun a pop-up dirty tech house set at the @bunkerclubdc afters. 

Only got mistaken for Calvin Harris 3 times at the festival this time!

Continue to be in awe of the energy on these dance floors 🙏, thank you to everyone who turned out!

📸 by @ragoimages
Wearing @sib.somewhereinbetween

San Francisco that was a blast (off)! 🚀

Huge thanks to @thebadasstronauts for having me play the outdoor stage at the insanely packed 5000 person @velvet_sf Saturday night. 

Only the giant inflatable 🧑‍🚀 got a backstage pass.

Got to check The Midway off my bucket list.
Can’t wait to be back 🫶❤️

Who’s recreating a summer version of this photo with me next week in Aspen? 👀😏

My @p.l.a.y.h.a.u.s party is teaming up with the @waspenhotel for the first ever Aspen Pride. 

Join us for a PlayHaus takeover Saturday night followed by a disco pool party Sunday.

And stay all weekend for an amazing lineup with @dragonette, @crushclubnyc, and more!

W Hotel guests receive a free all-access pass. Or visitors can join with a suggested donation. 

Visit prideaspen.com to book a discounted room or to snag tickets.

Flyer photo by @ragoimages

Swipe Right ➡️
Can finally announce I’ll be playing my first major festival at @electriczoony this September! 

It seems so surreal. Feels like just yesterday I was playing for free at random dive bars. 

Ya bois @spencer_huff & I will be throwing down on the @dreamlandpride stage alongside @kaskade, @theblessedmadonna, @cocoandbreezy & more.

Huge shoutout to @jakeresnicow for creating a Dreamland takeover at a major festival. 

Grab your flights now ;)
Made it to Rave Disneyland 🏰

Hey I saw you from across la plaza and I really dig your vibe. 

12 days of European summer - Tomorrowland, Berlin, Ibiza, and Barcelona. 🌞🌞

Surprise b2b with the twins 🍈🍈

Last month got to play one of my fav disco house sets ever at @verythatparty in Chicago. The recording is up on SoundCloud now!

Returning to Chicago in one week for Market Days. I’ll be spinning all 3 days! 
🍖Fri - MEAT @ Radius
🍹Sat - DS Tequila 
🍬Sun - Market Days Festival Aldine Stage

Market Days you’ve done it again.

That was the sweatiest, sexiest venue I’ve played to date.

Thank you to all 1000 of you who brought the energy and let me giddily flail around in the birthplace of house music. 

Uploading the set soon! 🙌

Big props to @dustyrcarpenter @jakeresnicow @jsgano and everyone else who continue to create these spaces for us at such iconic venues.

It might be the last few weeks of summer but they’re going to be filled with some major firsts! 

8/26 - PlayHaus @ Catbird Rooftop Denver ft. surprise special guest
(first time booking a major artist for my party)

9/1 - Electric Zoo Festival New York
(my first major festival)

9/2 & 9/3 - Southern Decadence Afterparty
(first time in New Orleans)

Then I’ll be taking a month off for some much needed R&R and working on music 🎵🎶

You know it’s a good time when I whip out the stank face & double squiggly arms. 

Huge thank you to @wearegalantis and @musicanyc for having @spencer_huff & I stop by after Ezoo cancelled Day 1.

We know a ton of you were already waiting at the gates when they called it off. 💖💖

See you again soon New York

📸 by @by.monti @dne.media

Was blessed to have @jworra stop by last month’s @p.l.a.y.h.a.u.s. Definitely one of the kindest & most talented artists I’ve ever met. Love seeing fellow Denverites killing it. 

The 2nd to last PlayHaus of the year at @catbirddenver rooftop is Saturday!

Excited to be headed back to Miami for NYE!

Come ring in the New Year with me at @dreamlandnye along with @purple_disco_machine, @trixiemattel, @anabelenglund & more!

DreamlandNYE.com

Step into my office…

📸 @simplyhao
